---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Us | Prime Appliance Repair" description="Learn about Prime Appliance Repair LLC - your trusted local appliance repair technicians in Troutdale, OR.">

  <!-- Page Header -->
  <section class="page-header">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>About Prime Appliance Repair</h1>
      <p>Local expertise. Honest service. Repairs done right.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Story Section -->
  <section class="story-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="story-grid">
        <div class="story-content">
          <h2>Our Story</h2>
          <p>Prime Appliance Repair LLC was founded with one simple goal: provide honest, reliable appliance repair that the East Metro Portland area could actually count on.</p>
          <p>We saw too many homeowners get burned by repair shops that overcharged, took weeks to schedule, or fixed the symptom instead of the problem. We built something different — a one-person shop where Anton handles every job personally, giving each customer the attention they deserve.</p>
          <p>As an appliance repair technician with years of hands-on experience, Anton has seen it all. From ancient dryers that should've been retired to brand-new refrigerators with factory defects. That experience means faster diagnoses, fewer repeat visits, and repairs that actually last.</p>
          <p>We treat every customer's home like it's our own. We show up on time, we clean up after ourselves, and we don't upsell services you don't need.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="story-image">
          <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1560250097-0b93528c311a?w=600&q=80" alt="Anton - Appliance Repair Technician" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Values Section -->
  <section class="values-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>What We Stand For</h2>
      <div class="values-grid">
        <div class="value-card">
          <div class="value-icon">🤝</div>
          <h3>Honesty First</h3>
          <p>We'll tell you the truth even if it means losing a job. If your appliance is worth repairing, we'll say so. If it's time to replace it, we'll tell you that too — and mean it.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card">
          <div class="value-icon">⚡</div>
          <h3>Respect Your Time</h3>
          <p>We show up when we say we will. We finish jobs efficiently. We don't waste your day with unnecessary appointments or follow-up visits for problems we could've caught the first time.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card">
          <div class="value-icon">🔧</div>
          <h3>Do It Right</h3>
          <p>Quality parts, proper repairs, and thorough testing before we leave. We'd rather spend an extra 20 minutes getting it right than have you call us back next week.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card">
          <div class="value-icon">💰</div>
          <h3>Fair Pricing</h3>
          <p>Our rates are competitive for the Portland metro area. We quote upfront, we don't add hidden fees, and we'll explain every line item on your invoice.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card">
          <div class="value-icon">🛡️</div>
          <h3>Accountability</h3>
          <p>Every repair comes with a 30-day warranty. If something we fixed breaks again, we come back and fix it at no charge. That's how confident we are in our work.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card">
          <div class="value-icon">🏠</div>
          <h3>Your Home, Our Priority</h3>
          <p>We wear shoe covers in your home, clean up our work area when we're done, and leave your space exactly how we found it — only cleaner, because your appliance is working again.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Promise Section -->
  <section class="promise-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="promise-box">
        <h2>Our Promise to You</h2>
        <div class="promise-list">
          <div class="promise-item">
            <span class="promise-check">✓</span>
            <span>No diagnosis fee if you proceed with the repair</span>
          </div>
          <div class="promise-item">
            <span class="promise-check">✓</span>
            <span>Upfront pricing before any work begins</span>
          </div>
          <div class="promise-item">
            <span class="promise-check">✓</span>
            <span>30-day warranty on all parts and labor</span>
          </div>
          <div class="promise-item">
            <span class="promise-check">✓</span>
            <span>Same-day or next-day scheduling</span>
          </div>
          <div class="promise-item">
            <span class="promise-check">✓</span>
            <span>Licensed, insured, and background-checked</span>
          </div>
          <div class="promise-item">
            <span class="promise-check">✓</span>
            <span>We text you when we're on the way</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="cta-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cta-box">
        <h2>Ready to Work Together?</h2>
        <p>Whether it's a broken refrigerator, a dryer that won't heat, or a dishwasher making strange noises — we're here to help.</p>
        <div class="cta-btns">
          <a href="tel:+15033893142" class="btn btn-accent">📞 (503) 389-3142</a>
          <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-outline-white">Contact Us</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
  .page-header {
    background: var(--primary);
    color: var(--white);
    padding: 4rem 0;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .page-header h1 {
    font-size: 2.75rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .page-header p {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    color: #bfdbfe;
  }

  /* Story */
  .story-section {
    padding: 5rem 0;
  }

  .story-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .story-content h2 {
    font-size: 2.25rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .story-content p {
    color: var(--gray-500);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .story-image {
    border-radius: 12px;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
  }

  .story-image img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 500px;
    object-fit: cover;
    display: block;
  }

  /* Values */
  .values-section {
    background: var(--gray-100);
    padding: 5rem 0;
  }

  .values-section h2 {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 2.25rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .values-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .value-card {
    background: var(--white);
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 12px;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .value-icon {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .value-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .value-card p {
    color: var(--gray-500);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* Promise */
  .promise-section {
    padding: 5rem 0;
  }

  .promise-box {
    background: var(--dark);
    color: var(--white);
    padding: 4rem;
    border-radius: 16px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .promise-box h2 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .promise-list {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 1rem;
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: left;
  }

  .promise-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
  }

  .promise-check {
    width: 24px;
    height: 24px;
    background: #16a34a;
    color: white;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  /* CTA */
  .cta-section {
    padding: 0 0 5rem;
  }

  .cta-box {
    background: var(--primary);
    color: var(--white);
    text-align: center;
    padding: 4rem;
    border-radius: 16px;
  }

  .cta-box h2 {
    font-size: 2.25rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .cta-box p {
    color: #bfdbfe;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }

  .cta-btns {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .btn {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.875rem 1.75rem;
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 1rem;
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }

  .btn-accent {
    background: var(--accent);
    color: var(--dark);
  }

  .btn-accent:hover {
    background: var(--accent-dark);
  }

  .btn-outline-white {
    background: transparent;
    color: var(--white);
    border: 2px solid var(--white);
  }

  .btn-outline-white:hover {
    background: var(--white);
    color: var(--primary);
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .story-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .story-image {
      order: -1;
    }

    .story-image img {
      height: 300px;
    }

    .values-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }

    .promise-list {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .promise-box {
      padding: 2.5rem;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .page-header h1 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .story-content {
      text-align: center;
    }

    .story-content h2 {
      text-align: center;
    }

    .story-content p {
      text-align: center;
    }

    .values-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .value-card {
      text-align: center;
    }

    .promise-list {
      text-align: center;
    }

    .promise-item {
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .cta-btns {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
    }
  }
</style>
